.custom-pg.business-page
  .row-fluid#business
    %h2{:id=>"business-page"}
    .span2

    .span8.text-center.page-3
      %p.top-2
        CASHHOPPERS FOR BUSINESS
      %br
      %br
      %br
      .row-fluid
        .span6.text-left
          .p
            The CASHHOPPERS game is a great tool to add to your marketing
            and advertising mix. SPONSOR a HOP item, and drive players to your
            booth, building or web site. ADVERTISE within the app and reach
            players with promotional opportunities, product discounts or brand
            messages. You can also create private HOPs - for your customers
            only - to highlight new products, grand openings, or any other
            big news that will have your customer base HOPPIN!
            %br
            %br
              Find out how to use CASHHOPPERS to your bussiness's advantage.
            %br
            %br
              = link_to 'LEARN MORE', '#',:class => 'btn btn-warning span6'
            %br
              = link_to 'SIGN ME UP', new_user_registration_path,:class => 'btn  btn-success span6'
        .span6.text-left
          = image_tag 'home_business.png', :class => 'business-img',:width=>"70%" ,:height=>"70%"


    .span2

.page-divider
